io.cloudboost

Class ACL

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.cloudboost.ACL

  • public class ACL
extends Object
    ACL-Access Control Lists is a wrapper around CloudBoost access and permission management system. It forms part of every record, file,data saved in the database. This enables fine-grained control over access to all resources in the App
